Initiative
Speed die

AC
Based on speed rank
S - 18
A - 10
B - 8
C - 6
D - 4
E - 2

HP
Equal to persistance score

To Hit
Roll precision rank die
for each 4 above the necessary to hit vaue an aditional Destructive power die is rolled

Crits
if a die crits you can roll the die again and add the new value rolled to the initial number

Wounds
1. shaken
2. incapacitated/ deaths door rolls
